    <body>
        <section name="Multiple source/output directories">
            <p>
                If you want to use more than one <a href="../compile-mojo.html#sourceDirectory">source</a> or
                <a href="../compile-mojo.html#outputDirectory">output</a> directory, then you must to configure multiple executions.
            </p>
            <pre>&lt;project&gt;
   ...
   &lt;build&gt;
      &lt;plugins&gt;
         ...
         &lt;plugin&gt;
            &lt;groupId&gt;${project.groupId}&lt;/groupId&gt;
            &lt;artifactId&gt;${project.artifactId}&lt;/artifactId&gt;
            &lt;version&gt;${project.version}&lt;/version&gt;
            &lt;executions&gt;
               &lt;execution&gt;
                  &lt;id&gt;lesscss-common&lt;/id&gt;
                  &lt;goals&gt;
                     &lt;goal&gt;compile&lt;/goal&gt;
                  &lt;/goals&gt;
                  &lt;configuration&gt;
                     &lt;sourceDirectory&gt;src/main/less/common&lt;/sourceDirectory&gt;
                     &lt;outputDirectory&gt;target/css/common&lt;/outputDirectory&gt;
                  &lt;/configuration&gt;
               &lt;/execution&gt;
               &lt;execution&gt;
                  &lt;id&gt;lesscss-vendors&lt;/id&gt;
                  &lt;goals&gt;
                     &lt;goal&gt;compile&lt;/goal&gt;
                  &lt;/goals&gt;
                  &lt;configuration&gt;
                     &lt;sourceDirectory&gt;src/vendors&lt;/sourceDirectory&gt;
                     &lt;outputDirectory&gt;target/css/vendors&lt;/outputDirectory&gt;
                  &lt;/configuration&gt;
               &lt;/execution&gt;
               ...
            &lt;/executions&gt;
         &lt;/plugin&gt;
      &lt;/plugins&gt;
   &lt;/build&gt;
&lt;project&gt;</pre>
        </section>
    </body>
